5 treasurer, secretary, and one member-at-large; and
6 c. Up to four (4) ex-officio, nonvoting members from recognized national
7 athletic trainer organizations.
8 3. The compact commission may remove any member of the executive
9 committee as provided in the compact commission’s bylaws.
10 4. The executive committee shall meet at least annually:
11 1. Executive committee meetings shall be open to the public, except that the
12 executive committee may meet in a closed, non-public meeting as provided in this
