16 interest in the business of the compact commission.
17 3. The executive committee may hold a special meeting in accordance with this
18 section.
19 E. The compact commission shall adopt and provide to the member states an
20 annual report.
21 F. Meetings of the Compact Commission:
22 1. All meetings shall be open to the public, except that the compact
